title: Macquarie University League club
body:
Hi all!
ok so im just starting uni this year and i went to the clubs page of Macquarie uni and i found out that they dont have a league club. I just wanted to write this discussion to see if anyone would actually be keen to join i dont know the details (figure that our along the way) but yeah.... just reply of this page and ill get back to you (^_^)

replies.body:
Hey there,

This board is for Help & Support regarding technical issues with the game, your thread would be better suited for the [Clubs](http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/clubs) board.
